{"id":254637,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-湖南上访维权者刘华等17人被警方送久敬庄/","date":"2012-10-02T15:31:08Z","modified":"2012-10-02T15:31:08Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南上访维权者刘华等17人被警方送久敬庄关押（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张勇报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分</span><span>左右，湖南上访维权者刘华等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>人，在北京 东方 君悦大酒店退房，被警察以查身份证为由，招来黑保安，将他们</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>人强行送进一辆车牌为“京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B12614</span><span>”的大巴。后上来两名黑保安，在警察的眼皮底下，殴打了老人李仲瑜。大家向现场警察求助但警察不理睬。访民们要求去派出所做笔录被警察拒绝。警察将他们全部送往久敬庄关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据刘华介绍：他们要求警察说明带走他们的理由，警察拒绝回答。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据刘华说：他是因遭遇强制拆迁，后四次进京上访，其中三次被截访；又发视频、写博文揭露当局，被以“诽谤”华远集团总裁任志强为由行政拘留；出来后状告公安，却经历尴尬的缺席审判，因而再次走上上访路。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>人，也大多都是因被强制拆迁，而去北京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>联系电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13873197043</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-_W3dj6PwMeI/UGrlPTtApYI/AAAAAAAAQMM/Zw91-SheePY/s1600/%E5%88%98%E5%8D%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%ACB12614%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%8A%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%A4%E4%BD%8D%E9%BB%91%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E3%80%82%E6%9D%8E%E4%BB%B2%E7%91%9C%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E9%BB%91%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E6%AC%A7%E6%89%93..jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-_W3dj6PwMeI/UGrlPTtApYI/AAAAAAAAQMM/Zw91-SheePY/s320/%E5%88%98%E5%8D%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%ACB12614%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%8A%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%A4%E4%BD%8D%E9%BB%91%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E3%80%82%E6%9D%8E%E4%BB%B2%E7%91%9C%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E9%BB%91%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E6%AC%A7%E6%89%93..jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>刘华等人被拖上大巴，两位黑保安殴打李仲瑜老人</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-HueRQcc7f_c/UGrlR0ZYoLI/AAAAAAAAQMU/lGWQr7HEvAw/s1600/%E4%BB%96%E4%BB%AC%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E9%80%81%E8%BF%9B%E4%B9%85%E6%95%AC%E5%BA%84%EF%BC%8C%E7%A9%BF%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%91%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%94%BE%E8%B5%B0%E3%80%82.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-HueRQcc7f_c/UGrlR0ZYoLI/AAAAAAAAQMU/lGWQr7HEvAw/s320/%E4%BB%96%E4%BB%AC%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E9%80%81%E8%BF%9B%E4%B9%85%E6%95%AC%E5%BA%84%EF%BC%8C%E7%A9%BF%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%91%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%94%BE%E8%B5%B0%E3%80%82.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>大家被强制送进久敬庄关押</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OwrYb3HaSlc/UGrlWgsA01I/AAAAAAAAQMc/y-sbOv1XYOg/s1600/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%88%E6%9D%A5%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86%E6%9F%A5%E6%88%BF%E7%9A%84%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OwrYb3HaSlc/UGrlWgsA01I/AAAAAAAAQMc/y-sbOv1XYOg/s320/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%88%E6%9D%A5%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86%E6%9F%A5%E6%88%BF%E7%9A%84%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>中午到宾